      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still doing this. everything just fell apart today. the lab results, the funding news... it's like my whole life was built on a foundation that just vanished. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. i feel like i'm running on empty and there's no finish line in sight. i just want everything to stop.",
